    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, producing a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip through corners. The chassis remains composed with solid subframe mounting and responsive dampening. Recent preventative maintenance includes the replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators, critical for long-term engine health. While the paint exhibits minor stone chips typical of spirited road use, the interior bolsters remain supportive and the mechanical synchronization is excellent. This is a mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the apex.",
